rows.label: tlk42200121_03_msg0001
rows.name:
The works of art in this city
are truly eye-opening, mo!

rows.label: tlk42200121_03_msg0002
rows.name:
As expected of Gula, the
land that has produced so
many famous painters, mo!

rows.label: tlk42200121_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I heard that the woodblock print of
Bahn-sama that I saw the other day was
also made by a famous Gulan carver, mo.

rows.label: tlk42200121_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I want to ask my mother to buy one
for me to display in my room, mo.

rows.label: tlk42200121_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Bahn-sama is a skilled merchant
that Popipii admires, mo.
